get-prime-factors
=================

Get prime factors.

## Installation
```
npm install get-prime-factors --save
```
## Usage
```
import getPrimeFactors from 'get-prime-factors';
getPrimeFactors(91); // [7,13]
getPrimeFactors(127381); // [17,59,127]
```
## Tests

  npm test
